description:
This set includes 1/4", 3/8", and 1/2" drive ratchets, with lengths of 3.54", 4.13", and 5.31" respectively. The compact design of these ratchets saves space and makes them easy to operate, even for people with large hands. Our mini ratchets exceed the ANSI standard.
These stubby ratchets are made of premium chrome vanadium steel and have a fully polished chrome-plated surface with a stylish thread design. They are corrosion-resistant, easy to wipe clean, and non-slip.
The ratchet head has a reversible 72-tooth gear that only needs a 5-degree swing arc to operate. The quick-release reversible head design allows you to replace the socket by simply touching the middle part, and you can change the driving direction by flipping the biased drive switch.
The quick-release head of the ratchet wrench can lock the socket firmly and prevent it from accidentally falling off. The offset switch ensures that the gear perfectly engages, preventing slipping and free-wheeling.
The 1/4 inch drive ratchet is perfect for disassembling small screws in furniture and household appliances. The 3/8 inch drive is suitable for auto repair, motorcycles, and electric vehicles, while the 1/2 inch drive is ideal for automobiles and motorcycles.

description:
About this item

Aluminum Alloy
【Great Compatibility】This Katerk 1/4 inch hex shank bit holder is specifically designed for 1/4 inch hex shank drill bits. It's compatible with most 1/4 fast hex handles, hex sockets, various electric screwdrivers, and handheld screwdrivers. The bit holder makes it a valuable addition for any handyman.
【Secure and Safe】Built with a secure backup nut design, each drill bit holder securely locks onto your bits, ensuring they stay firmly in place. Additionally, our bit holder incorporates a high-quality steel ball rolling design that holds up to several kilograms of weight, ensuring your various drill bits don't fall off.

Whether you're preparing food or serving guests, Keechee’s thoughtful design ensures hassle-free handling.

description:
About this item

Meal Prep MVP - A practical and innovative way to dice, slice, julienne, grate or spiralize your vegetables and fruits. With the Ultimate Chopper/Slicer & Spiralizer, preparing your favorite dishes for your whole family is no longer a chore. Made with premium materials like grade 420 stainless steel blades and food-grade bpa-free materials, it's the perfect tool to make home cooked meals easier and faster.
12 Diverse Blades - With nine interchangeable blades, the vegetable chopper offers the functionality of multiple kitchen tools all in one, unique kitchen gadget with a bonus adjustable Spiralizer for extra versatility. Make use of the 3 blade options of the Spiralizer for colorful veggie pasta, shapely salads, and gorgeous garnishes. The high-quality 2mm stainless steel slicer will create perfectly chopped onions, tomatoes, and peppers for salsa, or slice cabbage for coleslaw in no time.
Innovative Design - Free-up countertop space with the Food Container. Use the Food Holder while cutting small vegetables and fruits. This prevents food from slipping while slicing it. It also makes it clean, safe, and easy to work with. No more hassles of washing and wiping. Dismantle it and just put it in dishwasher. Cleans easily in minutes with the complementary scrubbing fork. Its compact size allows you to store it almost anywhere.
Improves Your Health And Saves Time – Busy lifestyles make us fall into the fast-food trap. It can take a lot of time and effort to dice, chop and slice the ingredients of a desired dish. Do not despair. Our multi-functional tool makes this process less time-consuming making it easier to add vegetables to your meals. That being said, you’re less likely to reach for unhealthy options. From now on, enjoy having more time for your family without missing out on any of the important nutrition.
Live Customer Care – Talk to us via out toll-free number or live chat, not by email like our competitors. Mueller believes in making life easier, better and more enjoyable in all that we do. Our unparalleled 24/7 live telephone customer support is ready and waiting to assist with anything you need!

description:
About this item

Comfortable to Use & Built to Last ✔ The Hand Grater has a razor-sharp stainless steel blade that won't rust and a comfortable, non-slip handle. Its unique curved sides make it extremely rigid and allow you to apply more force when it's needed.
Save Space in The Kitchen And Drawer ✔ Replace your bulky, unsafe, and hard-to-clean box grater, cheese grater electric, cheese grater with container or heavy electric food processor with a single Deiss Classic Zester Grater & Food Shredder. The metal parmesan cheese grater teeth won't clog up the way other graters for kitchen do, so it's a snap to clean. Just pass your cheese grader under running water.
Improve Your Cooking ✔ Amaze your friends with new, restaurant-like recipes. Add strong new flavours with fresh lemon zest without any bitter pith taste. When using the chef zester with hard cheeses such as parmesan, you'll get a nice pile of grated cheese that melts almost instantly on hot pasta.
Zesting & Grating Have Never Been So Simple ✔ Shear the hardest cheese into grated fluff or get nicely shredded carrots using almost no pressure. Simply zip the zest grater cutter-knife across the rinds of oranges, lemons, and limes. In seconds, you can have finely grated garlic or ginger or treat yourself to a favorite dessert topped with fluffy chocolate flakes.
Lifetime Warranty ✔ Deiss Kitchenware provides a lifetime warranty on its zesters for kitchen, grader for kitchen, rasp grater, zester grater with handle, carrot shredder, handheld cheese grater with handle. Plus you'll get the BONUS - exclusive "Healthy Cooking Tips" ebook - absolutely FREE!

description: A great go-to assortment of cookware must-haves, the Cuisinart Chef’s Classic 11-Piece Stainless Steel Cookware Set makes it easy to prepare multiple dishes at once. This essential set includes a 1.5 qt. Saucepan w/glass cover, 2.5 qt. Saucepan w/glass cover, 3 qt. Saucepan w/glass cover & helper handle, 8 qt. Stockpot w/glass cover, 8" skillet, 10" skillet and 7.08" steamer insert. Whether you’re looking to make hearty pasta, steam vegetables, or sauté, simmer, brown or fry, this premium stainless steel pots and pans set with aluminum encapsulated base heats quickly and spreads heat evenly, eliminating hot spots for optimal cooking performance. Cast stainless steel Cool Grip stick handles are contoured for a secure grip and designed to stay cool on the stovetop, while glass lids equipped with wide, easy-grip handles fit tight to lock in flavor, texture and nutrients. Riveted stainless steel handles, including side grips and helper handles, are professionally riveted to ensure a lifetime of perfect balance and a drip-free pour every time for your best cooking results. Easy to clean and conveniently dishwasher safe, this stainless steel cookware set is also oven safe up to 500°F and can be used on stovetop, in oven or under broiler, providing a range of versatile, professional performance.

Help Organize Your Kitchen and Pantry— Imagine every time walking to your kitchen or pantry, found everything is neatly organized. No longer messy, you can get everything you want very quickly. With the stackable and space-saving design, these containers will make more efficient use of every inch of your kitchen pantry cabinets.

24 Reusable Labels — Except 24pcs dry food storage containers, you will also receive 24pcs labels. They are reusable, you can switch contents whenever you need. Just wipe clean with a damp cloth to change what you have written, Peel and Re-stick.

description:
The Oxford Dictionary defines the paisley pattern as “A distinctive intricate pattern of curved feather-shaped figures based on an Indian pine-cone design.”

The iconic print is characterised by its bright and colourful, curved abstract figures. The design has been used in contemporary fashion and modern textiles for decades, and every colourway and variation of the pattern is entirely unique.

Famously worn by everyone from The Beatles, Queen and David Bowie to Victoria Beckham, the Paisley Pattern is a fashion staple.

Astercook 12-piece Pattern knife set is inspired by a time-honored and allegorical old decoration - Paisley Pattern. The intricate print gives the knife set its soft and rigid aesthetic, making it an indispensable practical and stylish kit for the kitchen.

About Astercook Knife Set

We have many years of experience in knife sets and are committed to providing our customers with the highest quality kitchen knives. With the goal of continuously improving the cooking experience of our customers.

Astercook 12-piece Paisley Pattern Knife Set

Paisley patterns were born in Babylon and flourished in Persia and India. Its pattern is said to be derived from the "tree of life" in Hinduism - bodhi leaves or date palm leaves. It seems to be inherently inextricably linked with myths such as "One Thousand and One Nights".

Today, the paisley pattern is widely used in various fashion designs and is a symbol of fashion.

Each Astercook 12-piece Paisley Pattern Knife Set comes in an exquisite gift box and is perfect for gift giving.

Non-stick - The coating on the blade makes food less likely to stick to the blade and can be easily rinsed off after use.
German High Carbon Stainless Steel - Astercook knives do not roll easily and are more durable than traditional stainless steel.
Sharpens Iron Like Mud - Each knife is precisely heat-treated to bring out the best qualities of the steel, making the blade very sharp.
Ergonomic Design - The whale-like streamlined handle fits perfectly in the palm of your hand. In addition, it allows you to hold it easily, reducing wrist fatigue.
Healthy - Thanks to the BO oxide layer, our knives are more anti-corrosion and less likely to harbor microorganisms than ordinary knives.
Safe Sheath - Each knife comes with knife sheath to protect you from cuts every time you pick it up or store it.

description:
About this item

COMPLETE 3-PIECE COLLECTION: This set includes large, medium, and small cutting boards, designed to handle all your chopping needs. Perfect for slicing fruits, dicing vegetables, preparing meats, or carving roasts. Use over the sink, on countertops, or outdoors for BBQ prep. A versatile kitchen essential that keeps your cooking space efficient, organized, and ready for anything from family meals to party spreads.
DURABLE BPA-FREE MATERIAL: Made from high-quality, food-grade polypropylene, these cutting boards are built to resist cracking, peeling, or splintering. Non-toxic and safe for daily use, they provide a reliable surface for preparing meats, vegetables, bread, and more. Designed for long-lasting durability, they protect your knives and make an excellent alternative to wooden or glass cutting boards.
NON-SLIP HANDLES FOR SAFETY: Each cutting board is equipped with textured grips that keep the board steady during chopping, slicing, and carving. Prevents slipping accidents and adds stability on countertops or sinks. Perfect for beginners learning to cook, busy families, or expert chefs needing reliable control. Makes food preparation safer and more comfortable in every kitchen environment.
EASY TO CLEAN, DISHWASHER SAFE: Save time in the kitchen with cutting boards that are simple to clean and fully dishwasher safe. Resistant to odors, stains, and knife scarring, they maintain a fresh and hygienic surface with every use. No warping or damage even after repeated washes, making them perfect for everyday cooking, holiday feasts, or meal prep for large families.
JUICE GROOVE DESIGN: Built-in grooves catch liquid from meats, fruits, and vegetables to prevent messy spills. Keeps countertops clean and drip-free while chopping juicy foods like tomatoes, watermelon, or freshly carved roasts. Helps reduce cleanup time, keeps your cooking area sanitary, and provides a neater, more organized food prep experience for every meal.
MULTIPURPOSE AND GIFT READY: Designed for versatile use as a meat cutting board, vegetable chopping board, or bread board. Doubles as a carving station for BBQs or serving tray for cheese and snacks. A thoughtful gift for weddings, housewarmings, college dorms, or holidays. Suitable for cooks of all levels, making it a practical kitchen essential and a reliable present for any occasion.

description:
SIMPLE TO USE & BUILT TO LAST: Our premium quality garlic chopper is constructed from food-grade, rust-resistant materials meant to be among your favorite kitchen gadgets for years to come. This garlic and ginger mincer is designed with built-in studs to extract more paste within seconds. It is great for both professional and home kitchens.
PEEL AND CRUSH EFFORTLESSLY: No more strong garlic odor or sticky residue lingering on your hands, as our silicone peeler does the job for you. Insert a clove inside the silicone and roll the sleeve vigorously over the counter with your palm to get the skin off the clove. Then use the ergonomic handle of the garlic mincer to crush cloves in one go by applying minimal effort.
EASY TO CLEAN: Simply rinse your garlic and ginger press tool under running water and use the included cleaning brush to get rid of any garlic bits or place it in the dishwasher for a quick clean up. We recommend rinsing the garlic crusher right after use to avoid residual pulp and fibers hardening up.
MULTI-PURPOSE TOOL: Don’t have a mortar and pestle? Fill the garlic mincer tool with coriander seeds, cumin seeds, or peppercorns when any recipe calls for “freshly cracked” or “coarsely ground” seeds. This garlic presser can also be used as a ginger press tool or to crush onions or nuts. Simply fill the chamber and squeeze to crush.
HASSLE-FREE, ZULAY GUARANTEE: We love and take pride in our ginger and garlic press and back this up with a lifetime warranty. We offer an incredible value at a moderate price and are confident that you'll love our garlic grinder! PROP 65 WARNING: This product may contain chemical(s) known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and/or other reproductive harm.

description: Created with the home chef in mind, T-fal Signature nonstick cookware provides an array of user-friendly features. Its innovative T-fal Thermo-Spot heat indicator simplifies pre-heating of pots and pans, which helps seal in the flavor of food, whether sautéing or searing. When the pattern in the center turns to a solid red spot, the pan is hot and ready to cook. The cookware’s heavy-gauge aluminum construction heats quickly and offers long-lasting strength, while its even-heat base distributes heat evenly for reliable cooking results. Use the cookware set on any kitchen cook top, except for induction. The cookware’s durable nonstick surfaces—inside and out—offer effortless food release, allowing to cook with little to no oil. The cookware’s vented tempered-glass lids trap in heat and moisture, while its ergonomically designed heat-resistant handles offer a secure, comfortable grip. Signature cookware is oven safe up to 350°F and dishwasher-safe, making it ideal for any kitchen. The 12 piece pots and pans set non stick includes 7.75 and 11 inch fry pans, 1 quart and 2 quart saucepans with lids, a 5.5 quart dutch oven with lid, a 10.25 inch griddle, a spoon, a ladle, and a slotted spatula. Enjoy cooking with Signature collection!

description:
About this item

34PCS KITCHEN UTENSILS SET WITH HOLDER From the everyday kitchen spoons to the garlic crusher, This 34PCS kitchen utensils tools set included all the kitchen stuff you could possibly need to bring out your inner chef. This means you don’t have to spend extra money on repetitive utensil tools. This cooking utensils set includes a Slotted Spatula, Slotted Spoon, Turner, Pasta Server, Kitchen Tongs, Grater, Scissors, and so on. It is a great starter pack for a first apartment
HEAT-RESISTANT, NON-MELTING-SOFT SILICONE One of the best things about Umite Chef silicone cooking utensils is their ability to withstand heat safely, each kitchen gadgetsl is heat-resistant up to a whopping 446°F and won’t melt (even leave it in the pot for a while) and our utensils head won't even become knicked or warped even at those extreme temperatures. The soft silicone won’t scratch non-stick cookware or your expensive pans
VINTAGE WOODEN HANDLE -EASY TO CLEAN Each wooden handle is made of solid wood which is anti scalding. Smooth and comfortable to the touch, it completely prevents the heat transfer during the cooking process. Please note that each wooden handle has a slightly different color and texture. The one-piece design eliminates any gaps where food can get trapped, making cleaning a breeze. PLEASE NOTE that due to the wooden handle, We don't recommend soaking in water for a long time or dishwasher cleaning
ODORLESS BPA-FREE, FOOD-GRADE SILICONE Each utensil is made of food-grade silicone, BPA-free, can use in any type of food. Stainless steel is wrapped inside to maintain its shape and flexibility, ensuring no warping. And it will not retain odors or colors like plastic kitchen utensils. ATTENTION Before the first use, the original smell will disappear after the silicone soaking in water and exposed it to the air for about 3 hours
GREAT PRESENTS SET This kitchen utensil set comes with everything you need to get started cooking. A utensils holder can help you organized your kitchen tools well. If you moving or just need a new set of cooking utensils highly recommended. Perfect for house warming presents, wedding presents, mother's day presents, holiday presents and anyone else on your presents list

Constructed of heat treated steel that is strong enough to avoid breaking while in use. The black oxide finish acts as a protective layer, can resist rusting well and increases the durability of the tool
Angled tip provides leverage for prying and lifting than the straight tip. Allow you to exert greater prying power between the 2 objects when you are trying to get apart. Especially when you are in confined spaces
Features Metal striking cap designed for hammering striking, allowing you to drive the tip into the tightest spaces. The cap fully contacts the end of the bar, so the force of each hammer blow is transferred directly to the bar itself
Comes with four protective end caps to keep tips sharp. When you need to remove baseboards, wall tiles, pry out nails or open stuck car doors. They are often the perfect tool for the job
Including 8 ", 12 " and 18 " for different situations. The shorter pry bar is ideal for tight spaces, and the longer one is perfect for a heavier object by offering you extra leverage. The 3 sizes allow you to always have the right tools in hand

description: Now Find Mark Electrical Boxes for Cutouts TWICE as Fast ; With NO Measuring! The Blind Mark electrical outlet box locator kit uses powerful rare-earth magnets to help you accurately locate and mark electrical outlet access holes for cutouts during installation of drywall, paneling and other materials, all with NO measuring required! description:
About this item

PREMIUM CONSTRUCTION – Each cookware is strong and durable yet lightweight and easy to handle. It is a work of art where form meets function. It is designed and constructed to exceed and outperform your expectations under any situation and at any skill level.
HEALTHY DURALON BLUE COATING – The eco-friendly, ultra-non-stick Gen10 Duralon Blue is all-natural ceramic coating free of harmful chemicals like PTFE, PFOA, lead, and cadmium and other toxic materials that can leach into your food. It also does not emit toxic gases at higher temperatures making them safe for you, your family, and the environment.
GENERATION 10 (G10) CERAMIC – Hardness is rated at 9H. It is exceptionally resistant to abrasion, corrosion, and acid meaning it won’t chip or discolor and will retain its non-stick properties longer. It heats fast and evenly; releases food effortlessly; and is extraordinarily durable.
PREMIUM METAL LIDS WITH FLAVOR CHANNELS – The premium metal lids are crafted with precision, featuring flavor dots designed for efficient moisture control. Each dot acts as a channel, redirecting moisture back onto the food like a gentle rain shower almost as if basting the food for maximum flavor.
PFAS FREE – All-natural ceramic coating is applied to the cooking surface making it non-stick, ensuring a cooking surface that is free from per- and polyfluoroalkyl substances (PFAS). Duralon Blue G10 Ceramic Coating was tested by TUV for 106 known PFAS elements, and none were detected.
ALL COOKTOP & OVEN SAFE – Every piece of the cookware set is induction ready and compatible with all cooktops including electric and gas. The cookware including the metal lids are oven-safe up to 500°F for seamless transition from stove to oven making them great for bread baking and roasts.

description:
About this item

PROTECTS FROM HOT SPITTING OIL - Our oil splatter guard shield securely joins to the handles of cookware to protect your hands from painful burns - Forget about hurtful blisters. No more need for potholders and oven mitts.
KEEPS THE STOVE, CABINETS, AND COUNTER CLEAN - Tired of cleaning stains off the wall, counter top, refrigerator, and cabinets? The frying pan splatter guard is a backsplash protector that will save you time cleaning and get you to your food while it's still hot.
WORKS WITH MOST COOKWARE - Our heavy-duty, grease splatter screen for frying pan fits most pots, pans and skillets – helping to protect you and your kitchen from hot snapping oil! Helps reduce kitchen odor.
NOT FLIMSY OVER FLAMES - Made from heavy duty stainless steel with an extra fine mesh. Unlike silicone alternatives, this oil splash guard allows steam to be released, while stopping 99% of splatter.
DISHWASHER SAFE - Our splatter guards for frying are dishwasher safe for hassle-free cleaning. Stays rust-free. Great for making schnitzel, french fries, hushpuppies, beignets, and burgers. Note: Take pan from heat to reduce sizzling when removing this stove splatter guard to flip or stir food.

About this item

【SUPERIOR QUALITY】 - The latest multifunctional vegetable chopper and slicer chop, dice, slice or grate! This vegetable chopper is a practical kitchen tool, the vegetable chopper offers multiple functions in one highly versatile kitchen gadget. The Onion Chopper is made of top quality materials such as high quality stainless steel blades and food grade materials. The vegetable chopper can cut most types of vegetables and fruits.
【8 INTERCHANGEABLE BLADES】- Vegetable Chopper Slicer contains 8 different sizes of fruit chopper blades interchangeable blades for thick/thin slicing, dicing or chunking, shredding/shredding, thick or thin, grinding and chopping. The chopper also makes it clean, safe and easy to use. No more hassle of cleaning and scrubbing. It can be easily cleaned in minutes with the matching scrubbing fork. Its compact size allows you to store it almost anywhere.
【IMPROVES YOUR HEALTH AND SAVES TIME】- Chopping, mincing and slicing ingredients for desired dishes can take a lot of time and effort, like tomatoes, cabbage, onions, garlic, etc. The new upgraded vegetable chopper reduces the time for the whole process, so you won't have trouble cooking or chopping vegetables and fruits. This makes it easier to add vegetables to your diet, adding variety to your family's meals and not missing out on any important nutrients.

description:
About this item

FOOD GRADE SILICONE BPA FREE!: Each cooking utensil is made entirely of food-grade silicone, BPA-free and odorless, We know that this is a health issue that concerns you and your family, and it is also the most important concern for every consumer. So We strictly control the production and quality of these cooking utensils. NOTE: It must be soaked for half an hour when it is used for the first time, and then exposed to the air for about 3 hours, the original smell of silica gel will disappear
STAINLESS STEEL CORE & NO GAPS, ONE PIECE DESIGN: Each cooking utensils has a stainless-steel core to ensure long-term deformation and durability. Soft silicone outer layer will not scratch your pan, At the same time, the silicone with a fine particle feel is also anti slip, providing you with a comfortable grip. The stainless steel is wrapped in silicone to form a whole seamless silicone design, You don't need to worry about cleaning issues caused by any welding seams
HIGHLY HEAT RESISTANT: One of the best things about Umite Chef silicone spatula kitchen utensils is its ability to withstand heat safely, each utensil is heat-resistant up to whopping 446°F and won’t melt (even leave it in the pot for a while) and our spatula head won't even become knicked or warped even at those extreme temperatures. This silicone cooking utensils does not react with food or beverages, Will not retain odors or colors when you use it for stirring based food products
EASY TO CLEAN &100% DISHWASHER SAFE: Seamless silicone design which is a major plus as there aren't any cracks or ridges to catch food or harbor anything that makes it super easy to clean. The sturdy silicone surface eliminates the worry about damage caused by machine washing to the product, Just put it in the dishwasher after use, and you will get a new set. This cookware utensils set has everything you need, It’s ideal presents for Mother’s Day, Christmas, as a housewarming present and more
VERSATILE 22PCS KITCHEN UTENSILS SET: we have selected this 22PCS silicone cooking utensil sets for you that is dedicated to cooking. This means you don’t have to spend extra money on repetitive utensil tools. Essential kitchen Tools Includes 1 x Ladle,1 x Pasta Fork,1 x Spoonula, 1 x Slotted Spoon,1 x Kitchen Tong,1 x Slotted turner,1 x Whisk,1 x Brush,1 x Large Spatula,1 x Small Spatula,1 x Egg Separator,1 x Holder, 5 x measuring spoons, 5 x measuring cups

description:
About this item

Storage Solution – The Chef Power removable cookware set makes kitchen storage simple. When stacked, it measures only 13 x 12 x 8 inches, reducing space usage by up to 70%.
Healthy Ceramic Nonstick – Chef Power’s ceramic coating, made from natural rock, is Teflon-free and free of PFAS, PTFE, PFOA, lead, and cadmium.
Compatible with All Stoves – The cookware is suitable for induction, gas, electric, and ceramic stoves, and it is oven-safe up to 550°F. The silicone lids are oven-safe up to 350°F, and the sealing lids can withstand temperatures from 170°F down to -100°F.
Easy to Clean – The double-sided ceramic nonstick coating on the pans and pots makes cleaning easy, and the set is dishwasher-safe.

ZEST, SHRED, SLICE, GRATE: say goodbye to endless kitchen tools and hello to the 4 in 1 all purpose cheese grater; 4 sides allow you to grate, shred, zest and slice nearly any food with ease; use on vegetables, fruits, chocolate, bread, cheeses, and just about anything else to create delightful recipes
STAINLESS STEEL CONSTRUCTION: the sharp, high quality stainless steel blades on all 4 sides of the cheese grater help grate, shred, zest and slice your foods quicker than ever; rust resistant and dishwasher safe for long lasting use
OVERSIZED ERGONOMIC DESIGN: comfortable and ergonomic handle of the cheese grater allows for a soft and slip resistant grip while you prepare meals; the extra large size makes it effortless to use; measures at 5 by 3.1 by 9.2 inches, making it oversized and easier than most others to use
STAYS IN PLACE: slip resistant border easily grips counters and food prep surfaces to help it stay in place
DETACHABLE CONTAINER: a detachable container with a removeable lid attaches seamlessly to the bottom of the grater so that you can catch and store ingredients easily; it includes measurements to help you get a precise measurement every time

description:
About this item

Healthy Ceramic Coating: Crafted from natural ceramic, this cookware set is completely free of intentionally added PFOA, PTFE, PFAS, lead, and cadmium. No toxic fumes—even when overheated. Cook safely and confidently for your whole family.
Ultra Nonstick Surface: The outstanding nonstick ceramic coating provides easy food release of this pots and pans set.Requires only a teaspoon of oil – Ideal for healthy, low-fat cooking.
Easy to Clean: Rivet-free nonstick surface wipes clean instantly.Dishwasher safe (hand wash recommended for longevity).
Compatible with All Stoves: A high magnetic conductive stainless steel base allows our nonstick cookware to work on all cooktops, including induction. Reinforced die-cast aluminum heats quickly and evenly while ensuring long-lasting durability—all in a lightweight design. Oven safe up to 550℉ (remove handle first).
Complete 16 Pcs Family Set: This cream white nonstick ceramic cooking set includes everything your kitchen needs: a 9.5" frypan and a 12.5" frying pan, an 11" / 4.5qt sauté pan with lid, a 1.5qt saucepan and a 2.5qt saucepan with lid, a 4.7qt casserole with lid, 2 silicone utensils, and 5 reusable pot protectors.
Thoughtful Design: Tempered glass lid for easy monitoring and preventing splashes on your stove. The woodgrain bakelite handle is comfortable to hold and remains cool while cooking.
Practical Gift: If you're seeking for a gift for your family or friends, our nonstick ceramic cooking set would be perfect for Mother's Day, Father's Day, Valentine's Day, Christmas, New Year, and house warming gifts new home, wedding gifts.
Building a Green Future Starts in Your Kitchen: Built to last and designed to be fully recyclable, these pans support a healthier lifestyle and a cleaner planet—cutting carbon emissions by up to 80%. When it's time for a replacement, the pan itself is fully recyclable—supporting a cleaner, circular future.

description:
About this item

【Why Choose ROYDX Stainless Steel Cookware Set】Flavor preservation. Heat transfer. Durability. Strength. Hygienic.
NO RISKY COATING: ROYDX stainless steel cookware does not contain harmful coatings such as PFOS, PFOA and PTFE. When cooking with ROYDX pots and pans, you'll be able to preserve and enhance the natural flavors of the food you're preparing.
TRI-PLY CLAD METAL CONSTRUCTION: The stainless cookware is a 3-ply design layering 430 stainless steel, aluminum, and 18/10(304) stainless steel. This layering helps to seal in the aluminum – so you don’t need to worry about leaching – while harnessing aluminum’s better heat conductivity to produce a more homogenous cooking surface.
DURABILITY: When it comes to cooking equipment, stainless steel is one of the most durable materials. The ROYDX stainless steel pot set will last for years and will not rust, chip, dent, crack or stain under normal use. Even better, stainless steel is generally dishwasher safe and can handle being stored in the refrigerator.
STRENGTH: ROYDX Pots and Pans Set is highly sought after because it retains its strength at both very high and very low temperatures. Oven-safe up to 572℉, glass lid 350℉. Being able to withstand high temperatures is very important when it comes to cooking appliances.
HYGIENIC: One of the greatest reasons to opt for ROYDX stainless steel cooking gear is that the material is very hygienic. Better yet, it is easy to clean and maintain, making post-feast cleanup a breeze. A regular scrub with an all purpose cleaner is all it takes to keep the metal gleaming.
ULTIMATE ADAPTATION: The stainless steel pot bottom with ultra strength & durability and is compatible with all stoves, including induction, gas, electric, halogen, glass and ceramic. At the same time, you don’t have to worry about the pot handle being too hot, because this set of pots is equipped with two removable handles, which is very convenient.

SPACE-SAVING SOLUTION: Neatly stack all the pots and pans, saving 75% of cabinet space—keeping the kitchen organized and tidy. Perfect for compact kitchens and an ideal choice for RVs or campers.
SET INCLUDES: 3 x Removable handles, 10&11 inch frypan, 11-inch steamer, 2 x sauce pans(2 & 2.5-quarts), 4.5-quart saute pan, 3 x fridge storage lids(2 ,2.5& 4.5-quarts), 3 x glass lid with silicone ring(2 ,2.5& 4.5-quarts), 5 x pot protectors.

Show more

description: Chambord is a true original – the classic French press Coffee maker designed in the fifties. And we still produce it with the same painstaking craftsmanship we used way back when with the original. The frame and lid, made of steel, undergo several Chrome Plating processes to obtain a durable shiny surface that will last for many years of intense use. The only difference in the production process since the fifties is our commitment to the highest standards of environmentally correct manufacturing, which is especially important during the Chrome Plating process. The black CHAMBORD polypropylene handle comes in a matte finish that not only gives a comfortable grip while serving but adds to the classic quality of the design. The French press system has always been the simplest and ultimate way of brewing an excellent cup of Coffee. Using fresh coarse ground beans with water between 92 and 96 degrees Celsius brings out the very best in all types of Coffee.

Wash in warm, soapy water before first use and dry thoroughly.

description:
Complete Kitchen in a Box: This kitchen cookware set provides everything you need to cook like a pro right out of the box. The set includes an 8-inch frying pan, 10-inch frying pan, 10-inch round grill pan, 3-qt saucepan with glass lid, 5-qt everyday pan with glass lid, 8-qt stockpot with glass lid, steamer, silicone ladle spoon, mixing spoon, pasta fork, and turner. Enjoy the convenience and versatility of having a complete set of cookware at your disposal.
9H Diamond-Level Enhanced Coating: The coating achieves 9H hardness, ensuring exceptional resistance to wear, corrosion, and acids. Please note that our ceramic coating serves as an alternative to Tef*l*on. While it’s equipped with ultra non stick feature, it's not *chemically* nonstick.
100% Healthy & TöxinFree: Completely safe, free from harmful chemicals like PFAS, lead, and cadmium. The ceramic coating provides a nonstick surface without releasing töxic gases, even at high temperatures, ensuring a healthy and eco-friendly cooking environment.
Far-Infrared Ray Active Release Technology: Enhance your cooking with advanced technology that improves food and water quality by removing töxins, maintaining freshness, balancing body pH, reducing radiatiön exposure, eliminating bad odörs, and minimizing food ällergies.
Rapid & Even Heat Distribution: The high-pressure stamped, thick-gauge pure aluminum base ensures rapid and even heat conductivity from end to end. Say goodbye to uneven cooking caused by dead zones or hot spots. Enjoy precise and consistent heat distribution, allowing you to achieve professional-level results with every dish. From searing to simmering, the DUXANO cookware set delivers consistent heat balance for flawlessly cooked meals.
Cool Touch Insulated Stainless Steel Handles: The unique handles are designed to stay cool to the touch, allowing you to handle the pans safely while cooking. The Y-shape design ensures comfort and ease of use for both right-handed and left-handed users. Remember to hold the far end of the handles to avoid burns when using fry pans or saucepans. Oven mitts or pot holders are recommended when handling the stockpot.
Premium Forged Construction: The 14-piece kitchen cookware set features premium forged construction, combining strength, durability, lightweight, and easy handling design. This perfect fusion of form and function performs exceptionally well in any cooking situation and is suitable for all skill levels. Experience the artistry and functionality of our high-quality cookware.

description:
The bella 9-Piece Ceramic Nonstick Cookware Set is the perfect blend of functionality and space-saving design, ideal for home chefs who want performance without sacrificing kitchen space. Each piece nests together, saving up to 50% more space, making it perfect for any kitchen, big or small. Available in four stylish colors—Oatmilk, Surf, Plum and Black—this pots and pans set complements any kitchen décor and is a thoughtful addition to wedding registries, housewarming gifts, new apartments, or even college dorms.
Crafted with our EverGood™ Ceramic Nonstick Coating, which is free from PFAS, PFOA, PTFE, lead, and cadmium, you can cook with confidence knowing that your meals are healthier and your cookware is eco-friendly. This versatile set includes a 2qt saucepan, a 5qt saucepan, a 10" deep wall fry pan with a helper handle, and a 3.5qt sauté pan—perfect for creating a wide range of dishes. Imagine whipping up a vibrant Moroccan tagine, a rich and creamy Thai coconut curry, or a colorful Spanish paella, all with ease.
Compatible with all stovetops, including induction, and oven safe up to 325°F, this non stick pots and pan set offers flexibility and convenience. Plus, cleanup is a breeze with dishwasher-safe pieces, though hand washing is recommended to maintain their pristine condition. The cooking set is not just a practical addition to your kitchen—it’s a stylish, thoughtful gift that’s perfect for any occasion.

description:
About this item

[Not just make it, we upgrade it.] We are a professional kitchenware producer who have been focus on customer experience. In order to offer better kitchenware, U-Taste collects customer suggestions of all similar products on Amazon. And then upgrade the products based on the data of the bad evaluation with the aim to provide customers with better kitchenware products.
[Food Grade Non-Stick Silicone] U-Taste uses superior material which is food grade, flexible and nonstick. Do not melt or release odor when cooking at high temps. We also handled the surface so they will not get dirty or look dirty after they are cleaned. The silicone handle also provides a firm solid smooth grip.
[480°F high temperature resistant] U-Taste uses superior material - the same material as baby nipple, which is Food Grade and can tolerate high temperatures up to 480°F. You can use this nonstick silicone spatula in a hot pan without worrying about melted plastic in your dinner. It also works well with high temp sugars, chocolates or sauces. A must for newer cooks who might tend to leave utensils in a nonstick pot while cooking.
[Right amount of blade flexibility for effective scraping] You may be sick of silicone either too stiff or too soft. These spatula utensils seriously strike the great balance. Slight flex at the tip, that moves into a nice sturdy handle. They are well balanced in the hand and do an excellent job of blending even dense material like bread dough. It's pliable enough to get into corners and conform to the shape of the pan or bowl, and get every last drop of food out of container smoothly.
[Seamless integrated design for easy cleaning] Are you tired of the handle of your current two-piece silicone spatula frequently separating? Now, try this dishwasher safe seamless utensil set, you don't need to worry about it coming apart and crevices for dirty stuff to hide. With flat surface, great for spreading frosting or icing on a cake.

features: SQUEEZE OUT EVERY DROP OF JUICE: Our 2-in-1 lemon squeezer won’t waste a single drop from your favorite fruit! We have designed this lime juicer to be easy on hands. Watch limes, lemons, and small oranges beg for mercy, even with a soft squeeze. The holes at the bottom of the citrus juicer serve as a seed filter to prevent the pulp and seeds from getting in your way.

SAVE TIME AND SPACE: You no longer have to worry about power, replacing batteries, or even bulky juicers crowding your kitchen counter with our easy-to-store citrus squeezer. Quench your thirst by making a citrusy lemonade or margarita in seconds; simply place a half cut lemon/lime in the bowl and watch the citrusy goodness add flavor to your drink or meal.

STURDY AND HEAVY DUTY BOWLS: This durable manual juicer is made from aluminum and is finished off with a food-grade coating, making it a perfect addition to your cocktail accessories for years to come. The ergonomic handle makes the lemon lime squeezer super comfortable for even kids to use.

CLEANS IN SECONDS: After adding a tangy flavor to your recipe, simply toss the citrus juicer in the dishwasher for a quick clean up. Our juice press can also be effortlessly cleaned by running it under water.

HASSLE-FREE, ZULAY GUARANTEE: We love and take pride in our lemon and lime squeezer and back it up with a lifetime guarantee. If there are ever any issues, just contact us, and we will make it right. Chances are that you will end up getting one for your friend too.

description:
About this item

NEVERSTICK DIFFERENCE: Won’t stick, chip or flake. Super-heated at 30,000°F, plasma ceramic particles are fused to the surface of the pan, creating a super-hard, textured surface that interlocks with our exclusive coating for a superior bond
HARD-ANODIZED EXTERIOR: This premium cookware has an extremely durable shot-blasted, hard-anodized exterior that resists scratches like stainless steel.
OVEN SAFE: Easily go from stovetop to oven to finish cooking meats, brown toppings, or bake like you can in cast iron. Lids, handles and nonstick coating are all oven safe up to 500°F.
PREMIUM DESIGN: Stainless-steel handles are ergonomically designed for comfort and double-riveted for strength and maneuverability. The tempered glass lid has a 13-mm-thick stainless-steel rim to lock in moisture and ensure maximum visibility.
IMPROVED HEAT RETENTION: The heavy-gauge 4.5 mm aluminum base is designed to prevent hot spots and to enable quick, even heat distribution for perfect results every time. Contains 30% more aluminum than Ninja Foodi NeverStick Essential C100 series.
SEARS LIKE STAINLESS: Sear like you can in stainless steel, without needing additional oil or butter. Plus, sauté, griddle, pan fry, shallow fry, braise, bake, roast, and broil with this multifunctional cookware set.
EASY CLEANUP: NeverStick cooking surface wipes clean and is easier to clean than traditional stainless pans.

SAFE & EASY TO USE: Nonstick coating is metal-utensil safe, easy to wipe clean and dishwasher-safe. Made with only FDA-approved food-safe materials. All range capable: compatible with gas, electric, glass ceramic, and induction stoves.
WHAT’S INCLUDED: 8'' Fry Pan with Glass Lid, 10.25'' Fry Pan with Lid, 12'' Fry Pan, 1.5 qt. Saucepan with Lid, 2.5 qt. Saucepan with Lid, 3.5 qt. Saucepan with Lid, 3 qt. Sauté Pan with Lid, 4 qt. Stock Pot with Lid & 8 qt. Stock Pot with Lid.

description:
EVERYTHING YOU NEED From the everyday kitchen spoons to the garlic crusher, we included all the kitchen stuff you could possibly need to bring out your inner chef. This means you don’t have to spend extra money on repetitive utensil tools. This cooking utensils set includes Slotted Spatula, Slotted Spoon, Turner, Pasta Server, Solid Spoon, Kitchen Tongs and other kitchen tools such as Pizza Cutter, Grater, Can opener, Scissors and so on. Almost everything you need in a kitchen is in one box.
MORE SAFE AND HEALTHY&ODOR-FREE Each kitchen utensil is made with a 100% food grade silicone head, BPA-free, and no harsh chemical odoro. We know that this is a health issue that concerns you and your family, So We strictly control the production and quality of these cooking utensils. NOTE: It must be soaked for half an hour when it is used for the first time, and then exposed to the air for about 3 hours, the original smell of silica gel will disappear
HARD WEARING &DURABLE WITH FLEXIBILITY soft silicone features incredibly flexible and beveled edges that make flipping easier than ever; slides easily under a variety of foods. The abrasive silicone head material does not scratch as easily as plastic, The stainless steel is wrapped in silicone to form a whole body, which is soft without warping and bending. The soft silicone tip protects your non-stick pan. The ergonomic stainless steel handle provides you with a comfortable cooking experience
HIGHLY HEAT RESISTANT One of the best things about Umite Chef silicone spatula kitchen utensils is its ability to withstand heat safely, each utensil is heat-resistant up to whopping 446°F and won’t melt (even leave it in the pot for a while) and our utensil head won't even become knicked or warped even at those extreme temperatures. This silicone cooking utensils does not react with food or beverages, Will not retain odors or colors when you use it for stirring based food products
EASY TO CLEAN & GIFTS: These silicone kitchen utensils are very easy to clean. Please not to put in the dishwasher with other dishes that are heavily stained with oil to Prevent white water stains on silicone utensils. After being soaked in water for 5 minutes, they will become very clean after being rinsed with water. Please not to put in the dishwasher with other dishes that are heavily stained with oil to Prevent white water stains on silicone utensils

All skillets are made from recycled aluminum with healthy ceramic nonstick material to reduce carbon dioxideemissions by 80%.

description:
About this item

Large Capacity: Organize your kitchen drawer and make more space with this silverware organizer. Comes with two expandable panels on the left and right to store more silverware, cutlery, and kitchen utensils.

description:
About this item

GLAMORIZE YOUR KITCHEN – Dive into the art of culinary finesse, with our nonstick chef essential set, comprising of a set of 3 Frying Pans, measuring 8 inch, 9.5 inch and 11 inch.
HARBORING A CULINARY HAVEN – Explore new recipes and savor the delectable aroma, with the impeccably fabricated, nonstick even-heat distributed frying pans, Omelette Pan, ideal for all types of cook-tops, be it electric or ceramic.
SPICE UP YOUR COOKING AURA – The wobble-free bakelite handles are artistically designed and firmly riveted to the pans, for safety and comfort.
KITCHEN MAGICIAN IN YOUR HANDS – Cherish a blissful cooking experience with this garnishing-flavor set, perfect for simmering pasta sauces, sautéing vegetables, flipping pancakes, stir-frying meat or reheating any leftovers.
EASY CARE - Let the hot cookware cool down before washing. Avoid the usage of harsh detergents or abrasive materials to wash. Always dry the cookware after use, it is recommended to use soft cotton or linen for drying. The cookware is dishwasher safe however, it is recommended to hand wash.
The Bakelite handles are ergonomically designed and riveted strongly to the pan for safety and comfort.
